Template: mastodon-image-poster/image_directory
Type: string
Default: /srv/images
Description: Directory containing images to post:
 Please enter the full path to the directory containing images that
 should be posted to Mastodon.

Template: mastodon-image-poster/sort_order
Type: select
Default: name
Choices: name, size, time
Description: Image sorting order:
 Choose how images should be sorted before posting.
 name = alphabetical, size = by file size, time = by creation time.

Template: mastodon-image-poster/instance_url
Type: string
Default: https://mastodon.social
Description: Mastodon instance URL:
 Please enter the URL of the Mastodon instance to post to.

Template: mastodon-image-poster/access_token
Type: password
Description: Mastodon API access token:
 Please enter the access token for the Mastodon API.
 You can generate one in Mastodon under
 Preferences > Development > New application.

Template: mastodon-image-poster/status_text
Type: string
Default:
Description: Status text for each post (optional):
 If empty, the image filename (without extension) will be used as
 the status text.
